Maintainer: Tobias Schulze <tobias.schulze@ufz.de>
Description: REcoTox is a semi-automated, interactive workflow to process
    US EPA ECOTOX Knowledgebase entire database ASCII files to extract and process
    ecotoxicological data relevant (but not restricted) to the ecotoxicity groups
    algae, crustaceans, and fish in the aquatic domain. The latest version of
    the ASCII files is available on US EPA ECOTOX Knowledgebase.
    The focus is aquatic ecotoxicity and the unit of the retrieved data is mg/L.
